        {
            "title": "美國和伊朗據悉考慮延長停火 霍爾木茲海峽局勢仍高度緊張",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Institute for the Study of War and AEI’s Critical Threats Project as of April 15 morning Middle East time\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"835\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/shSeJ79qUNiQHIPM85U5iA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/aeabc85f9d8f02a0f5b8594b13661bc0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Institute for the Study of War and AEI’s Critical Threats Project as of April 15 morning Middle East time</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，美國與伊朗正考慮將停火延長兩周，以爭取更多時間推進和平協議談判。儘管圍繞霍爾木茲海峽的對峙加劇，但此舉有望降低戰爭重燃的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的這位知情人士表示，調解方正尋求開展技術性會談，以解決阻礙在下周停火到期後達成更長期協議的關鍵分歧。相關問題包括重開霍爾木茲海峽以及伊朗核計畫的未來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">霍爾木茲海峽的局勢仍然嚴峻。美國設立了海上封鎖以切斷伊朗運輸，而德黑蘭繼續限制其他船隻通過該海峽。這種對峙導致航運量大幅下降，加劇了能源供應危機並威脅對全球經濟造成重大衝擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c59e3388-27db-33de-bc62-d99d7fbb15df-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"觀看：美國和伊朗考慮延長停火來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k9PF0DLKV66ax1FxNlJylg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2e8ff7095fe67413cf1a08f4f007b76b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：美國和伊朗考慮延長停火來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊之間的戰鬥在4月8日左右開始暫停，當時美國總統唐納德·川普在前一晚宣布達成為期兩周的停火。上周末，雙方在巴基斯坦舉行了首輪和談，但包括美國副總統JD·范斯在內的與會者未能促成協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國尚未「正式請求延長停火」，白宮新聞秘書卡羅琳·萊維特周三對記者表示，但承認「我們仍在積極參與這些談判」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巴基斯坦軍方表示，該國代表團周三抵達伊朗，伊斯蘭堡繼續在雙方之間傳遞信息，發揮調解作用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據伊朗國家電視台，伊朗聯合軍隊總部指揮官Ali Abdollahi表示，伊朗認為美國的持續封鎖是「違反停火的前奏」。他表示，如果封鎖繼續，伊朗武裝部隊「將不允許波斯灣、阿曼海或紅海的任何進出口繼續進行」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"835\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fBZHEmLH0.CgpZhJKiiW7w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cafb52c2ac420dc69a1dbf68248b2114\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管以色列上周與美國一道暫停對伊朗的攻擊，但以軍仍在黎巴嫩打擊伊朗支持的真主黨。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以色列總理內塔尼亞胡周三晚些時候表示，在部隊打擊真主黨目標之際，他已經指示軍方繼續擴大黎巴嫩南部的安全區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US, Iran Weigh Truce Extension With Hormuz Still Shuttered (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Patrick Sykes.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E4%BB%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-201309943.html",
